{"tid":2367193,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"消息稱油麻地廿幢大廈強制檢測　有商戶憂疫區標籤效應","createTime":"2021-01-15T06:46:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-15T07:03:35.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4aa2c10458f76675f386133d5ba77340fd182f6d","tid":2367193,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T06:46:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1570590-20210115.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1570590-20210115.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=ZtPc16BOUua4x2eUEWBZFhckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=ee675e0d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1570590-20210115.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=9e0227aa\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1570590-20210115.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n消息指，政府將多幢位於油麻地佐敦一帶的樓宇納入強制檢測範圍，只要大廈內有一宗新型肺炎確診個案，就要接受強制檢測，預料涉及20多幢大廈數千名居民。<br />\n<br />\n有一宗確診個案的炮台街46號，大廈地舖售賣蔬菜的老闆黃先生認為，新措施太嚴厲，擔心一次過將20多幢樓宇納入強檢範圍，會造成標籤效應，令人誤以為整個油麻地佐敦都是疫區，附近街市近日人流已經很冷清，擔心生意進一步受影響。<br />\n<br />\n居於炮台街46號的居民簡女士說，贊成擴大強檢範圍，自己會按規定接受檢測，但質疑作用不大，因為即時這一刻病毒測試呈陰性，下一刻可能會受感染。"},{"pid":"dcf9005ac57f89528c3d91fcb87b16f50da53f02","tid":2367193,"uid":77196,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T06:46:58.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"red\">因為即時這一刻病毒測試呈陰性，下一刻可能會受感染。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e03856daf84ed73b01e76f75a94765e6fbf8ce4c","tid":2367193,"uid":45910,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dcf9005ac57f89528c3d91fcb87b16f50da53f02","tid":2367193,"uid":77196,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T06:46:58.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"red\">因為即時這一刻病毒測試呈陰性，下一刻可能會受感染。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T06:49:11.000Z","msg":"驗孕可以避孕是常識吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4db94792e06197f22ad87f44f7176d7b73311cb","tid":2367193,"uid":185492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dcf9005ac57f89528c3d91fcb87b16f50da53f02","tid":2367193,"uid":77196,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T06:46:58.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"red\">因為即時這一刻病毒測試呈陰性，下一刻可能會受感染。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T07:03:35.000Z","msg":"明明綠燈，轉眼便是紅燈"}]}